Message.Title=Next {Case.Name} payment.
Message.OverPayment.Title={Case.Name} over payment.
Message.UnderPayment.Title= {Case.Name} under payment.

Message.First.Payment=Your next payment is due on {Payment.Due.Date}.
Message.Payment.Latest=Your latest payment of {Payment.Amount} was due on {Payment.Due.Date}. Click {link:here:paymentDetails} to view the payment details. Your next payment is due on {Payment.Next.Date}. Click {link:My Payments:paymentHistory} to view your payment history.
Message.Last.Payment=Your latest payment of {Payment.Amount} was due on {Payment.Due.Date}. Click {link:here:paymentDetails} to view the payment details.
Message.Cancelled.Payment=Your payment of {Payment.Amount}, due on {Payment.Due.Date}, has been cancelled. Click {link:here:paymentDetails} to view the details. Click {link:Contact Information:contactInfo} to contact your case worker if you need more information. Your next payment is due on {Payment.Next.Date}. Click {link:My Payments:paymentHistory} to view your payment history.
Message.Reissue.Payment=Your latest payment of {Payment.Amount} was due on {Payment.Due.Date}. Click {link:here:paymentDetails} to view the payment details. This payment was originally cancelled on {Payment.Cancellation.Date}. Click {link:here:paymentCancelDetails} to view the cancellation details. Your next payment is due on {Payment.Next.Date}. Click {link:My Payments:paymentHistory} to view your payment history.
Message.Expired.Payment=Your payment of {Payment.Amount}, due on {Payment.Due.Date}, has expired. Click {link:here:paymentDetails} to view the details. Click {link:Contact Information:contactInfo} to contact your case worker if you need more information. Click {link:My Payments:paymentHistory} to view your payment history.
Message.Stopped.Payment=Your {Case.Name} payments have been stopped from {Payment.Stopped.Date}. Click {link:Contact Information:contactInfo} to contact your case worker if you need more information.
Message.Unsuspended.Payment=Your {Case.Name} payment suspension has been lifted from {Payment.Unsuspension.Date}. Your next payment is due on {Payment.Next.Date}.
Message.Overpaid.Payment = We have overpaid your {Case.Name} payments by {Payment.Amount}. Click {link:here:liabilityDetails} to view the details.Click {link:Contact Information:contactInfo} to contact your case worker if you need more information.
Message.UnderPaid.Payment = We have identified that we have underpaid your {Case.Name} payments by {Payment.Amount}. Click  {link:here:underPaymentDetails} to view the details.Click {link:Contact Information:contactInfo} to contact your case worker if you need more information.Click {link:My Payments:paymentHistory} to view your payment history.

